        "description": {
            "value": "<p><span>This set of healer’s tools contains a seemingly endless supply of bandages, herbs, and healing items of impeccable quality, granting you a +2 item bonus to Medicine checks.<br></span></p>\n<p><span><strong>Activate</strong> <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">A</span> Treat Poison or 8 hours (Treat Disease); <strong>Effect</strong> You can activate the tools when you use them to Treat Poison in order to produce the effects of @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.SUKaxVZW2TlM8lu0]{Neutralize Poison}, or when you Treat Disease in order to produce the effects of @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.RneiyehRO6f7LP44]{Remove Disease}. Once these medicines have been used to treat a patient’s poison or disease, they can’t be used again to treat the same affliction for that patient.&nbsp;</span></p>",
